---
title: Mexican Smokey Fish Tacos with Charred Corn & Rainbow Slaw
description: Pull up next to a beach in Mexico and you'll undoubtedly smell the delicious aromas of fish tacos. This homemade version  might be missing the ocean breeze, but still maintains the spicy, zingy and fresh flavours of the original creation.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5cac3cbec445fa0f966187f2-c38510e9.jpg
